ies mit den Grundlagen der Visual Culture und leistet so einen Beitrag zu einer Theorie der sozio-medialen Konstruktion von Behinderung.  aThis volume works through the photographic representation of disability historically that at the same time contributes to a theory of the social and media construction of disability.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aArchiv. 4aBild. 4aBildwissenschaft. 4aDisability Studies. 4aFotografie. 4aKunstwissenschaft. 4aMedienästhetik. 4aStiftung Liebenau. 4aVisual Culture. 7aART / Criticism.2bisacsh  aArchive.  aFine Arts.  aImage.  aMedia Aesthetics.  aPhotography.  aVisual Culture.  aVisual Studies.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2016z978311070100508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2016z9783110482812oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPP Plus eBook-Package 2016z978311070101208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839434949zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839434949423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839434949/original  a978-3-11-070100-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2016b2016  a978-3-11-070101-2  PP Plus eBook-Package 2016b2016  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DADb2016  aZDB-23-DGGb2016  aZDB-23-TGPc2014d2016